# StreamTech - Backend
```bash
    This microservice allows for centralized and secure management of streaming accounts,
    including Create, Update, Edit, Delete, and Assign operations. It provides a robust REST API
    to interact with data from external applications, featuring security through Spring Security
    and JWT (JSON Web Token).
```

#Technologies
```bash
    Java: 17
    Springboot: 3.2.5

    ### Tools
    SpringSecurity
    JWT
    Spring Data JPA & JDBC
    Loombok
    MySql
```

#  Installtion and Configuration
```bash
     1. Clone the project.
     2. Your environment variables must include:
         ${DATABASE}: Your database name
         ${USERNAME}: Your database user
         ${PASSWORD}: Your database password

         ${SECRET}: Your secret key to generate and sign JWT tokens
     3. Run your microservice
```